Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:15.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:26.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:45.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:52.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:59.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:05.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:13.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:20.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:26.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.05,0:01:34.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The technology\Nin my country, Shoukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:32.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is the most\Ncutting edge in Daikuuriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:37.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even so, we still can't build a plane\Nthat can fly above the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:43.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and if lightning struck the gas tank,\Nit would instantly explode into flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.46,0:02:47.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're aware of\Nthis danger but must go forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Beyond the waves' crests...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kyuukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:16.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,This sublime and peaceful\Ncountry carries a certain secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:22.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,To gain this secret, my country\Nhas mounted countless invasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we have always been thwarted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:42.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kyuukoku's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,The demonic Simoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,No other vessel in Daikuuriku\Nis capable of flying so freely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fallen Wings\N...throughout the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:56.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Fallen Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:27.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a routine patrol flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,The governors are observing today,\Nso they're making a show of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril-sama...\NCall her "Sibylla Aurea."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,She glitters like gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was your father well, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria, you're tormenting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are hundreds\Nof Ri Majon patterns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:02.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and depending on the mix,\Nthey take infinite shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've forgotten what many\Nof those patterns signify...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:10.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but the Simoun sibyllae are\Nalways prepared to rediscover them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:15.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is\Nan outstanding pilot, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,It seems she's become a\Nfull-fledged pilot, which relieves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:24.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Indeed, she's become the premier\NSimoun sibylla called "Sibylla Aurea."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:27.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her prayers may\Nindeed be exceptional...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:31.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but if she's used in war,\Nwe're only tarnishing an old tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,High Priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:37.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can we use prayers meant\Nonly for the gods for war?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:42.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,By deploying Simouns to the border,\Nwe display Tempus Spatium's power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:47.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and can repulse these nefarious\Ninvaders in a peaceful manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that not\Nin accordance with God's will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:08.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,My father made a point of ordering\NChor Tempest to mobilize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,...since he wanted to look\Ngood for the spectators.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:14.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because Chor Tempest\Nis the best chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:19.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria, it's not becoming of\Na sibylla to use the word "best."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:25.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're only offering up our prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:30.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,By achieving a perfect Ri Majon,\Nwe give comfort to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:33.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to become powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,More and more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Powerful? For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:50.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!\NDo you hear what I'm hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:29.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is Neviril of Chor Tempest.\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,They fell... Which Simoun fell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Caput has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are the only survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Send a messenger\Nto Guragief-sama right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:53.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun was shot down...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,We knew this day\Nwould come someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:30.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ever since the day they decided\Nto send us into battle with Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, Amuria.\NSimouns are divine aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,No matter what country\Ndevelops a flying machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:39.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they cannot match the craft of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:44.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why enemies flee\Nat the sight of a Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,They flee when they see us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:54.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are we going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:58.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I'm with you,\NPara-sama, I don't mind dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I still have things to do. I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:07.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did I allow such familiar\Naddressing, Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, we need your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:14.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're good? Shoukoku's\Nflying machines float like clouds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,There must be some mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:20.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no question.\NSimouns can't fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:23.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,We just fly them,\Nand the enemy runs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sublime harmony...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:29.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, let's try the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:34.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,That again. We don't have the ancient\NRi Majon patterns fully analyzed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:38.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibyllae of legend succeeded\Nwith an Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:41.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and served as priestesses\Nclose to Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we succeed,\Nwe can end up that way too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:49.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're so impatient. Now isn't\Nthe time to think of such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:52.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to become more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:56.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's the border. I'm taking us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:24.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are divine aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:28.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,True, the technology is on\Na whole different level than ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if we can discover their secret,\Nour country will make great advances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Falcon Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they dare to enter our country,\Nthen they'll never leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:26.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're just flying after all.\NThey're not like Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Simoun inscribes patterns upon\Nthe sky using the light from its wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:39.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't yet discovered\Nwhy it's so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:46.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once we find out this secret,\Nour nation's technology will advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:53.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Kyuukoku has long kept\Nthe secrets of the Simouns from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:59.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been taught that Simouns\Nsend those who pursue them to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:03.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,But now I see.\NThe Simouns are mere machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:05.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no hell in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can there be so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:18.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns aren't divine aircraft.\NThey're just machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:22.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,So they can fall.\NIt's possible to shoot them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:26.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Someday we'll solve\Nthe Ri Majon mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:31.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,The era of Kyuukoku's monopoly\Non Simoun technology will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:35.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,There are a lot, but they're slowpokes!\NShoot them all down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shark Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Six-unit Iron Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:53.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll erase the glyph!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:14.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they fail to draw a glyph,\Nthey can't achieve a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon, Neviril.\NA miracle is sure to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, Amuria.\NThere's no telling what will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:37.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to become stronger.\NI want to become stronger, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:41.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't go on like this!\NSo many things getting in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're taking our wings away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right... We've got to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:57.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said I want to become stronger.\NYou understand, right, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.49,0:14:59.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:19.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go. To where we can be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:16:00.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, more... More powerful, Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:17.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don't look! You can't\Nkill them if you see their eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.65,0:16:27.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:29.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:50.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium is full of fury.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:54.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not divine aircraft at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:17:00.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,My country will surely\Ndiscover this demonic secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,But could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they really were...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:28.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea is exhausted.\NI'll relay your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,...leaving the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:42.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,We intend to go to\Nthe Spring to meet with Onasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you go, you can't be a sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:49.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll never be able to touch\Na Simoun again. You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI intend to become a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,To become just as gallant as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:59.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's unseemly to speak of\Nsuch intentions to others. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to stare at\Nher door forever, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am unable\Nto assuage a sibylla's grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I can do is grieve just as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you a trainee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:43.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the sanctuary\Nof the sibyllae. Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are the priestesses\Nin better humor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:52.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Should the moon be covered\Nby clouds, the stars fade too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's where they stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:58.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,They have lost a precious pair.\NThey're not to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:05.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest has lost three sibyllae.\NNot counting those going to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meaning it is no longer our elite chor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dux.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Floe. Sibylla Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually, this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:22.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's young, but we're having her join\NChor Tempest as a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:31.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is most irregular. Promoting\Nsuch a young trainee to sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if we don't, we'll no longer\Nbe able to protect the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,So is that doll your only replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, there's one more before launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another oddball?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another oddball?\NNo, a normal one, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:05.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow! This is a Simoun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen the real thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:11.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aer?\NI expected you to arrive sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Shoukoku's planes are advancing\Nalong the border once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:26.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sending Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:31.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Neviril won't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:37.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't see Neviril and Paraietta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,They won't want to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:45.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have nothing but\Nthe Simouns to fight with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:49.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,But is it God's will that\Nwe do something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:54.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:56.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please wait, Sibylla Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's probably not a priestess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:20.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's a Simile training craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That can't achieve a Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:36.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rest of you can go on praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've come here to go into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.29,0:22:53.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.03,0:22:58.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:05.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.31,0:23:13.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:25.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.98,0:23:38.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:44.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.89,0:23:50.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.39,0:23:53.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:59.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:05.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:18.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns can't\Npossibly fall, and yet they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Blue Spring\NNext time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Blue Spring\NThe Blue Spring.
